The '''University of Garos''' was located in [[Ariana]], on [[Garos IV]]. It contained a large number of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] records that survived the data purges initiated by [[Ysanne Isard]]. As such, after Garos joined the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], following the [[Thrawn campaign]], New Republic historians and scientists swarmed to the University's databanks.

